{"tid":2192021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"只准檢測不許投票「明眼人都知打壓」  抗爭者歸隊 高呼重啟選舉","createTime":"2020-09-07T00:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T00:59:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7e714dfc87063bb5c8affcd38af7059ccaa98f","tid":2192021,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:17:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/3AYFQ3QK5JF5FMEOOTWWOFJRRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2F3AYFQ3QK5JF5FMEOOTWWOFJRRE%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=62b3db54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2F3AYFQ3QK5JF5FMEOOTWWOFJRRE%2F&h=cf1bb88d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/3AYFQ3QK5JF5FMEOOTWWOFJRRE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n只准檢測不許投票「明眼人都知打壓」 <br />\n抗爭者歸隊 高呼重啟選舉<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】原是四年一度立法會選舉投票日，卻被政府借疫情剝奪，人民只好由票站走出街頭。響應網民號召上街的群眾批評，港府掠奪公民投票權，又以國安法打壓港人，但他們不會畏懼，揚言至死一天都會堅持上街爭取人權公義。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃之鋒遭四車跟蹤 花個半鐘甩身<br />\n<br />\n油麻地至旺角一帶昨日民心湧動，舉起「香港人團結」紙牌的吳婆婆說，政府押後選舉，剝奪市民投票權利，惟有盡良心上街抗議，「要爭取我哋嘅權利&hellip;&hellip;𠵱家已經一國一制，我哋再唔爭取就冇喇香港」。她說已做足被捕的心理準備，無懼國安法，堅持上街發聲，「直至我瞓低死咗&hellip;&hellip;一日生存都仲係要發聲，我要為我嘅子女、下一代爭取自由。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t2CX0Md1nG-gHqXfTElfNOuM_U4=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LGVRERLFVRFUTL3S2AUMVGNS5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft2CX0Md1nG-gHqXfTElfNOuM_U4%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLGVRERLFVRFUTL3S2AUMVGNS5E.jpg&h=08440601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■市民高舉「五一」手勢上街遊行，表達對政權剝奪立法會選舉的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倡立法會議員杯葛延任<br />\n<br />\n林小姐則說，上街是希望爭取盡快重啟公平公正的選舉，以及抗議港府種種打壓及不公，「已經冇晒言論自由、民主，又用國安法亂咁鎮壓我哋，無論點都會繼續出嚟。」她無法接受立法會議員以委任方式延任，「接受委任即係認同佢取消（押後）立法會選舉&hellip;&hellip;應該係要爭取雙普選。」對於被捕風險，她慨嘆「我哋好多手足死嘅死、拉嘅拉，佢哋咪仲慘？」<br />\n<br />\n阿樂及阿琪則結伴到佐敦「行街」，在港府種種打壓下，她們覺得唯一可做的就是上街發聲，阿樂認為政府禁止投票而推行全民檢測不合邏輯，「檢測中心好多都係cover返票站，邏輯上係講唔通，擺明就係打壓、明眼人都知。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社民連三人嗌口號被捕<br />\n<br />\n社民連主席黃浩銘、副主席梁國雄及成員陳皓桓等人昨下午2時許於佐敦逸東酒店外，拉起「押後選舉，與民為敵，政治篩選，誅除異己」的橫額，並叫口號要求重啟選舉。社民連批評港府以抗疫為。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方警告他們違反限聚令，要求他們解散，否則票控，雙方多次理論。陳皓桓、黃浩銘及梁國雄其後往旺角方向前行及高叫口號。警方以涉嫌參與未經批准集結，拘捕他們。社民連表示，三人被送往油麻地警署，被指涉嫌組織未經批准遊行及參與受禁群組聚集。<br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機日前呼籲港。。。。。。。。。。，樞機身體力行，昨日中午站在貼有「撤回決定」和「重啟選舉」標語前的空地，手持鐵煲及湯勺持續敲打一分鐘，附近的車輛亦有響號和應。<br />\n<br />\n網民在陳日君直播時留言支持，有教友亦在家中窗戶拍手分半鐘響應，「雖然整棟樓宇只有我一人拍手的聲音微不足道，但我信天子俯聽我們的聲音。」<br />\n<br />\n政府晚上發表新聞稿回應，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8eY6GMP2UD4Ow8OPwnM-S4YHQzE=/2277x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X5AVVPTI2FCOLDEHIHVPJRCWQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8eY6GMP2UD4Ow8OPwnM-S4YHQzE%3D%2F2277x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX5AVVPTI2FCOLDEHIHVPJRCWQI.jpg&h=c6845fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有遊行人士穿戴寫有標語的紙箱，宣示港人應享投票權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/INfwFgu6fWmT_pViAnv159Da3TM=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H7OHRFZPVZH7BB5HQDLKOXFTHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FINfwFgu6fWmT_pViAnv159Da3TM%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH7OHRFZPVZH7BB5HQDLKOXFTHU.jpg&h=8049847f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■社民連成員拉橫額抗議押後選舉，遭警方指控犯聚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jM0137hTYcQM7sU-TBsj6hryONs=/1197x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VR5VUTYQJRDPHCKLF2F3KXEZTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjM0137hTYcQM7sU-TBsj6hryONs%3D%2F1197x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVR5VUTYQJRDPHCKLF2F3KXEZTQ.jpg&h=058e6dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳日君昨在空地敲鐵煲發聲一分鐘，表達重啟選舉訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rG4HAgZtI_CkIvzJks5qvmfw1qE=/1773x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZUJT7TPGVBGOZL32FOQA6YTPSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrG4HAgZtI_CkIvzJks5qvmfw1qE%3D%2F1773x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZUJT7TPGVBGOZL32FOQA6YTPSY.jpg&h=a30b9dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■學生組織賢學思政成員被防暴警帶到封鎖線內截查，六人被捕。"},{"pid":"01ee4fdcad64a4a58b40e2182384750db34023e7","tid":2192021,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:19:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8caeca084386ae2627992c8ca8e1f2b06380a1c8","tid":2192021,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859d0c851aaa39782e1bfc0685a32e8fb18814b9","tid":2192021,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}